{"tid":850574,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人會 有時突然唔開心","createTime":"2018-10-06T15:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T14:57:40.000Z","uid":208916,"like":122,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"68f6f7f0339488007957ff64125a734557c4dec4","tid":850574,"uid":208916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:05:38.000Z","msg":"突然唔開心，唔想講野，<br />\n平時好鍾意食野嘅我，嗰段時間變得冇曬食慾 。<br />\n諗咩都好灰，一開口就係負能量，好驚咁樣冇曬朋友，連發脾氣都唔想發，即使人哋講錯野。<br />\n點樣死法都諗，但諗屋企人會傷心就打消咗念頭。<br />\n喺被竇入面喊，同埋會行行下街流眼淚，鼻子一酸((我諗唔到用咩詞語黎形容<br />\n呢啲情況最多2個禮拜，讀中學時期最長就3-4個月。。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇人一樣？ 有冇方法解決？<br />\n我想陽光啲，令周圍啲人開心。"},{"pid":"906a820be7e34d3f8c98f5667f8189b498a1c0af","tid":850574,"uid":147972,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:07:44.000Z","msg":"會 我都想自己樂觀啲 但生來如此"},{"pid":"05fd8b7bbd77a59ab16a48229ef0ffe3b7c5afe4","tid":850574,"uid":138138,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:09:35.000Z","msg":"急屎個時會唔開心"},{"pid":"b6973ecdfc67434d1dc9dfe81ef90c0220c930d4","tid":850574,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:18:50.000Z","msg":"你係咪major中文"},{"pid":"5ed91dff05ab9d629e20e1f166f6332ac0e92cfb","tid":850574,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:19:31.000Z","msg":"經常"},{"pid":"95cd2b315b1ab435a643282b5e3c8e309da5b878","tid":850574,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:19:57.000Z","msg":"ak<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be93c3ded6bda01ea87b34dee41bb7fe55cb30ee","tid":850574,"uid":186845,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:28:09.000Z","msg":"same here <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先要搵到壓力嘅源頭<br />\n其實諗真d 好多時候都係自己比壓力自己/身邊人對自己有期望 跟住就會覺得唔開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為左減輕壓力 我而家係咁洗自己腦<br />\n成日同自己講冇期望就冇失望<br />\n同埋唔會輕易作出承諾 費事要負多一個責任"},{"pid":"b078e571e91af6c92cce10adedaebe560b8ed2e2","tid":850574,"uid":145618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:46:32.000Z","msg":"明既 有時自己一個既時候就會有咁既諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c78aed5c7b64c2139f6da52b0b5f0c4d69ec91","tid":850574,"uid":213214,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:48:55.000Z","msg":"每次都好似m黎咁 (仆你個乖明明我男人黎<br />\n做乜都冇心機<br />\n個人冇哂希望<br />\n冇哂生存意義<br />\n淨係想快啲死<br />\n<br />\n點撚知隔幾日又正常返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21207304177072da3866ef74e53fad66427a7c37","tid":850574,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:50:00.000Z","msg":"會   人嚟架嘛  好正常啫<br />\n<br />\n成日都開心嗰班  先係最易痴線嗰班"},{"pid":"aa8cc4fcfc1204c2ed608ea4f48eaf821f7d7a8f","tid":850574,"uid":171119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:51:50.000Z","msg":"事出必有因<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無留意過每每發生/做左某d事你就會咁"},{"pid":"bdc2037abddb1cac7d9e6139d884137acee52680","tid":850574,"uid":148185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:51:52.000Z","msg":"會"},{"pid":"44c7dfcc82a84bd0cd7b5acae2c303d3c1973edc","tid":850574,"uid":208916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6973ecdfc67434d1dc9dfe81ef90c0220c930d4","tid":850574,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:18:50.000Z","msg":"你係咪major中文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T16:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對唔住 中文差 ，係咪睇唔明我講緊咩。。。。。。"},{"pid":"c146d823efe0df3ed11a524c6a0054590cec0740","tid":850574,"uid":208916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05fd8b7bbd77a59ab16a48229ef0ffe3b7c5afe4","tid":850574,"uid":138138,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:09:35.000Z","ms